 رَجَآء [رَجَاْي]<br>a. Hope, expectation.<br> b. Fear.<br> c. see)<br>رَجَي<br> (a), (b). <br> رَجِيَّة []<br>a. Hope, wish, desire.<br> <br> أُرْجُوَان<br> a. A certain red dye; redness; purple."}]}}